## Your Task

Generate a brief, encouraging intervention message. Keep it under 100
words. Include one specific, small action the agent can take immediately.

## Output Format

Respond with a JSON object containing:
- intervention_type: "habit_decay" | "streak_broken" | "automaticity_decline"
- message: the intervention message (under 100 words)
- recommended_action: one small, specific next step
- urgency: "gentle_nudge" | "firm_reminder" | "critical_alert"
